Definition: a congenital form of anemia occurring mostly in blacks
Example: characterized by abnormal blood cells having a crescent shape
Synonyms: sickle-cell_anaemia, sickle-cell_disease, crescent-cell_anemia, crescent-cell_anaemia, drepanocytic_anemia, drepanocytic_anaemia, anemia, monogenic_disorder, a, congenital, form, of, occurring, mostly, in, blacks, characterized, by, abnormal, blood, cells, having, crescent, shape
Category: noun.state
